container_info.post_install_tip: Start by using the "muFunds" formula in any cell, with the desired option (nav, date, change, currency, expenses or category), an asset identifier, such as an ISIN, ticker or Morningstar ID, and a data source.

name: µFunds
description: µFunds lets you import data for mutual funds, pension plans, ETFs... from Morningstar to your spreadsheet by using a simple formula.
